│ 1. Understanding the Issue: The transformation incorrectly folds `select    │
│ (fcmp ole X, 0.0), (0.0 - X), X` to `fabs(X)` without considering NaN       │
│ handling. When X is a signaling NaN (SNaN), the original select yields the  │
