│ negative could produce -0.0 when X is +0.0. That's a corner case. We'll     │
│ require nsz as well to be safe.                                             │
│                                                                             │
│ We'll add a condition before the transformation: `if (!SI.hasNoNaNs() ||    │
│ !SI.hasNoSignedZeros()) continue;`                                          │
│                                                                             │
